y isn't advanced enough. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usaevanjnoir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Saevan JNoir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/4/02 11:54:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22598.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: my point of view?</span><hr size=1> Actually, the Iksar society according to VI has no malcontents, the usual source for rogues. Of course, this is an invalid arguement, due to both the WE 'rogues' (scouts) and the fact that Kunark is loaded with Iksar bandits, 'rogue shaman', pariahs, etc.<br><br>/shrug<br><br>VI isn't really known for their consistancy, hehe. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=10371>Saevan J’Noir - Teir'Dal Blackguard</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ueuripedmoped.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Euriped Moped</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/4/02 12:10:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22598.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~yolora/zdance.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: my point of view?</span><hr size=1> Not being advanced enough is the reason verant put forth for there not being ikkie rogues. The malcontent theory is wrong for